description: This is a system generated manifest of files expected to be present in this zip. It can be safely deleted.

manifest.description: This is a starter notebook to help you make your first submission.
Is an example of what your submission file should look like. The order of the rows does not matter, but the names of the "ID" must be correct.
Train contains the target. This is the dataset that you will use to train your model.
Test resembles Train.csv but without the target-related columns. This is the dataset on which you will apply your model to.
